-os-4-oneplus-hybrid-wearables-smartwatches\"\u003egets handed off between the two\u003c/a\u003e, and the result is long battery life. It helps that there’s a 500mAh battery, too."},"dropcap":true,"endmark":false,"lead":false},{"__typename":"EntryBodyImage","placement":{"id":"K6rax7","alignment":"FLOAT_LEFT"},"__isEntryBodyComponent":"EntryBodyImage","contentWarning":"","image":{"url":"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/vluCcU91zPdTonSndLD4VhWJveg=/0x0:2700x1800/2700x1800/filters:focal(1350x900:1351x901)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25379975/247069_Oneplus_watch_2_AKrales_0096.jpg","height":1800,"width":2700,"hideCredit":true,"caption":{"html":"\u003cem\u003eI wasn’t able to view historical sleep data in the app with the original OnePlus Watch. Not a problem here.\u003c/em\u003e","plaintext":"I wasn’t able to view historical sleep data in the app with the original OnePlus Watch. Not a problem here."},"credit":{"html":"Photo by Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge"},"asset":{"title":"Look at OnePlus’ mobile app with sleep chart pulled up"}}},{"__typename":"EntryBodyImage","placement":{"id":"1IPIPb","alignment":"FLOAT_LEFT"},"__isEntryBodyComponent":"EntryBodyImage","contentWarning":"","image":{"url":"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/2oNDv7XS2YRiWPozPXgxLTHgn-M=/0x0:2700x1800/2700x1800/filters:focal(1350x900:1351x901)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25379976/247069_Oneplus_watch_2_AKrales_0108.jpg","height":1800,"width":2700,"hideCredit":true,"caption":{"html":"\u003cem\u003eI was so pleased to see that my data actually synced properly. The bar was low.\u003c/em\u003e","plaintext":"I was so pleased to see that my data actually synced properly. The bar was low."},"credit":{"html":"Photo by Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge"},"asset":{"title":"Dashboard view of OnePlus’ OHealth app"}}},{"__typename":"EntryBodyParagraph","placement":{"id":"c7DMIG","alignment":null},"__isEntryBodyComponent":"EntryBodyParagraph","contents":{"html":"How long depends on you